content: create a table about the books published by Vanessa fong. Here are the column titles and what information they include - title, title of the book, publisher - name of publisher, year published - the year published, number of pages - number of pages, major idea #1 - a description of a major idea from the book, major idea #2 - another major idea from the book, similar theorist - the names of one or more theorists who would largely agree with these ideas, including the names of books of theirs and quotes from the books showing this agreement, then contrarian theorists - the names of one or more theorists who would largely disagree with these ideas, including the names of books of theirs and quotes from the books showing this disagreement
